{"tid":2190715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本小學生的暑期自由研究 手繪介紹47都道府縣知事的口罩特色","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T04:19:59.000Z","uid":36494,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d21a16b5855922cbb09139891b3a3c62e578ca","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"日本小學多鼓勵學生們自行探索社會，因此假期時總會有一份自由研究（類似香港的專題研習）的功課，有的是小組進行、有的是個人自行完成。日本一位媽媽在Twitter分享了女兒介紹47都道府縣知事的口罩的自由研究習作，詳細的內容、可愛精美的插畫獲得不了少關注。<br />\n<br />\n封面除了用色豐富外，推主的女兒更畫出了各種常見的口罩類型：安倍的口罩、即棄口罩、布口罩、海棉口罩、面罩等等。（安倍的口罩：安倍首相常戴著不合自己尺寸的超小口罩因而惹來人民關注）<br />\n<br />\n擬訂題目的原因：知事們都戴著各式各樣的口罩<br />\n<br />\n她以漫畫的方式表述了以此為題的原因其實是受到電視上沖繩知事的啟發，發現知事們都戴著各式各樣的口罩，因此決定搜集47位知事的口罩造型，記錄在自由研究中。研究中她十分有條理地以都道府縣的編號排序，並畫出知事們的樣子、口罩款式，並記錄口罩的素材和特徵等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0VdJ3h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0VdJ3h.png&h=7187313d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CUYU90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CUYU90.png&h=7cfba352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FP1P1P6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFP1P1P6.png&h=d9216235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"431ce51bb9446adbedbc5f0df01f85a2175a8678","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"最時髦口罩排名<br />\n除了詳細介紹每一位知事於觀察日所佩戴的口罩外，她更選出了心目中口罩款式最時髦的三位知事，並附上一句點評。<br />\n<br />\n第1名：沖繩縣知事<br />\n點評：因為太常見白色口罩，而知事為它們添加了顏色。<br />\n<br />\n第2名：三重縣知事<br />\n點評：因為孩子們都喜歡的炭治郎（估計是指格仔圖案）。<br />\n<br />\n第3名：青森縣知事<br />\n點評：因為是青森特產的蘋果花紋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9id633F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9id633F.png&h=34c40fea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d6df858a8f0872dc3005817822bc68960206d3","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:43:11.000Z","msg":"第1名：沖繩縣 玉城康裕（玉城デニー）知事<br />\n玉城知事平常多數戴著妻子親手製作的布口罩（內附咖啡濾紙），口罩上的花紋主要是沖繩的傳統花紋（かりゆし）和動漫人物。<br />\n<br />\n玉城知事的口罩就像衣服一樣，沖繩時報曾為他的口罩造型製作組圖。<br />\n<br />\n玉城知事亦曾在Twitter上載自己戴著《JoJo的奇妙冒險》角色造型布口罩的相片，指是妻子和女兒合作製成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHmko30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHmko30.png&h=2bb65f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAXomQG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAXomQG.png&h=16113279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"877de64158819a38aba3cd33c8d7d64c514e36fd","tid":2190715,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"整得好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037637f7c43be245613fbd1c876bcc1dc3bea1e2","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"第2名：三重縣 鈴木英敬知事<br />\n<br />\n鈴木知事多數佩戴即棄口罩，但也會戴布口罩。推主女兒記錄了他於7月31日使用的格子口罩，花紋與動漫《鬼滅之刃》中炭治郎的外衣十分相似。<br />\n<br />\n8月初時鈴木知事亦有在Twitter指他於7月底戴過一次這款布口罩便引來很大回響，他介紹指口罩的確是參考了炭治郎的顏色設計，並由三重縣尾鷲市的社福設施「天使之家」製作。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他本人更親自回應了這個自由研究的帖文，感謝獲選時髦口罩第2名，並大讚這份研究十分出色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbkdJ4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbkdJ4p.png&h=3c25697a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GbgGQ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GbgGQ5.png&h=b7e0eb2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"790e26f0f5af2a191783ed9e9c4ce7ae3939d400","tid":2190715,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"好可愛 ! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a55d2944c454b84966eef401fd127f5bd2490e","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"第3名：青森縣 三村申吾知事<br />\n<br />\n推主女兒指三村知事的口罩看著很年輕也很可愛，像在為青森的特產蘋果賣廣告，亦指知事常常笑面迎人。她更留意到三村知事有數款不同的蘋果布口罩。<br />\n<br />\n一位網民亦曾上載三村知事戴著其中一款蘋果花紋口罩的新聞圖片，更指他平常已經很時髦，現在連口罩也很時髦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zwyu1Rr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwyu1Rr.png&h=19ee84d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSk1SX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSk1SX8.png&h=a3004c13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcce92d99a782951829e13c4d1e88073071266b1","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:47:12.000Z","msg":"胡鬧排名<br />\n<br />\n有款式最時髦的頭3名自然也會有最不濟的尾3名。（注意：第1名是倒數第1。）<br />\n<br />\n第1名：千葉縣知事<br />\n點評：因為內外反轉了。<br />\n<br />\n第2名：福岡縣知事<br />\n點評：因為也許是用了小童口罩。<br />\n<br />\n第3名：愛知縣知事<br />\n點評：因為面罩雖好但只用了2天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WqZetw1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqZetw1.png&h=d84f2890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3c2193cc202f632cbb136b8eddbc4aa325c05bd","tid":2190715,"uid":28808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86f438a9a81e32d73a9ab6d9a8ebe1a67ca2a63","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"第1名：千葉縣 森田健作（鈴木榮治）知事<br />\n<br />\n雖然森田知事是用即棄口罩，但佩戴口罩時竟然內外反轉了，成了全日本的笑柄。推主女兒更在圖畫旁細心標注口罩上的字：「這是裏面。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhifcZw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhifcZw.png&h=1d5d1002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4月6日森田知事的確在網絡上引起了極大回響，更被指是浪費了高品質的「三次元口罩」，更歎道明明口罩上內側已印著的提示字句。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第2名：福岡縣 小川洋知事<br />\n<br />\n小川知事雖使用即棄口罩，但因常常使用不合適的超小口罩而榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rcPhrr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rcPhrr.png&h=8c3f6b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3名：愛知縣 大村秀章知事<br />\n<br />\n大村知事平時會戴布口罩，亦會使用即棄口罩。5月時他曾在記者會上以透明面罩示人，又指「用面罩較易說話」；但2天後他又改稱「和相像不同，比起口罩更難呼吸」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwvpQME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwvpQME.png&h=e58cbecf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b80b59f41ebd44ad981a4a9635bf3066d8f8ec60","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"網民好評<br />\n<br />\n網民閱後大讚推主女兒十分能掌握每一位知事的特徵，研究內容有趣且觀察入微。<br />\n<br />\n「請向女兒轉述，她似顏繪十分能捕捉到特徵，調查內容亦很詳細，點評也有趣極了。<br />\n女兒加油呢」<br />\n<br />\n「最棒的自由研究！似顏繪亦十分拿手。」<br />\n<br />\n欣賞過推主女兒的作品後發現47位知事的口罩真的各有特色，將當地特產和吉祥品戴在臉上真的是超級好的宣傳，也為受疫症影響的現況添了一份生氣！由於推主女兒的自由研究太詳盡，本文未能盡錄，可到原帖欣賞全部內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/47-prefectures-mask-child/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2F47-prefectures-mask-child%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR34IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=f3f1c892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/47-prefectures-mask-child/</a>"},{"pid":"c5d45c26b991470359bacdecf425220456969eb6","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a8b2a168ae84e4f9b09acdd325452cfc284a0de","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8483708bb828fba38c39b0172786abe778f9a2f8","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"feea866146924ec1744e183beb4f0bcfbbb2ab51","tid":2190715,"uid":13504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港小學生暑期研究：<br />\n國安法的好處"},{"pid":"2aa5a7a417ba2fadd255af02d4c6e293f9547be6","tid":2190715,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d6df858a8f0872dc3005817822bc68960206d3","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:43:11.000Z","msg":"第1名：沖繩縣 玉城康裕（玉城デニー）知事<br />\n玉城知事平常多數戴著妻子親手製作的布口罩（內附咖啡濾紙），口罩上的花紋主要是沖繩的傳統花紋（かりゆし）和動漫人物。<br />\n<br />\n玉城知事的口罩就像衣服一樣，沖繩時報曾為他的口罩造型製作組圖。<br />\n<br />\n玉城知事亦曾在Twitter上載自己戴著《JoJo的奇妙冒險》角色造型布口罩的相片，指是妻子和女兒合作製成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHmko30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHmko30.png&h=2bb65f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAXomQG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAXomQG.png&h=16113279&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.custom-cursor.com/collections/155/coll_jojos_bizarre_adventure.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.custom-cursor.com%2Fcollections%2F155%2Fcoll_jojos_bizarre_adventure.png&h=6f18f680&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"899632b2902599cfe7ec46b90e1563ad147f4a8c","tid":2190715,"uid":77233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14a55d2944c454b84966eef401fd127f5bd2490e","tid":2190715,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"第3名：青森縣 三村申吾知事<br />\n<br />\n推主女兒指三村知事的口罩看著很年輕也很可愛，像在為青森的特產蘋果賣廣告，亦指知事常常笑面迎人。她更留意到三村知事有數款不同的蘋果布口罩。<br />\n<br />\n一位網民亦曾上載三村知事戴著其中一款蘋果花紋口罩的新聞圖片，更指他平常已經很時髦，現在連口罩也很時髦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zwyu1Rr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwyu1Rr.png&h=19ee84d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSk1SX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSk1SX8.png&h=a3004c13&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"呢個咁似講野甩假牙嗰條友嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}